                <h1>DUI and Background Checks: What You Need to Know</h1>
                <p>Yes, a DUI can show up on a background check, especially if it's criminal. Most employers conduct background checks to ensure a safe workplace, and any convictions could impact hiring decisions. Depending on the state, DUIs may remain on your record for several years. It's essential to understand your local laws regarding DUI expungement.</p>
